        "number": 22,
        "imagePath": "/oracle-images/oracle-5/22_icon.png",
        "description": "22\r\nAcorn\r\nGeneral\r\nNoun\r\nHoard\r\nVerb\r\nPreparing\r\nAdjective\r\nBuried\r\nAdverb\r\nHaphazardly\r\nQuestion\r\nYes\r\nDetailed \r\nAnswer\r\nYes, but only if you carefully \r\nremember.\r\nSocial\r\nGives the impression that they have information you \r\nneed.\r\nSocial\r\nRole\r\n  Bystander\r\nContext\r\n  Short Rest\r\nChoice\r\n  Gather Info\r\nResult\r\n  Helps\r\nCombat\r\nPicks a different target at random.\r\n  Random Encounter\r\nYou come across creatures who are gathering food for \r\nthemselves.\r\nCombat\r\nOutcome\r\n  Use / Defend\r\nCombat\r\nTargeting\r\n  Weakest\r\nRole\r\n  Soldier\r\nRole Size\r\n  Minion\r\nStance\r\n  Fresh\r\nQuest & Encounter\r\n  New Quest\r\nGather certain ingredients from a forest.\r\n  Quest Development\r\nThe location of the objective you seek has been lost to \r\nall involved.  You will have to discover another means \r\nof finding it.\r\n  Reward\r\nRare herbs.\r\n  Penalty\r\nYou realize your notes and maps are wrong; you lose \r\ntrack of one “known” location.\r\nQuest\r\nArchetype\r\n  Obtain\r\nSub\r\n  Gather\r\n33"
