        "oracleSet": 6,
        "number": 10,
        "imagePath": "/oracle-images/oracle-6/10_icon.png",
        "description": "10\r\nAbacus\r\nGeneral\r\nNoun\r\nCache\r\nVerb\r\nCounting\r\nAdjective\r\nCalculating\r\nAdverb\r\nPrecisely\r\nQuestion\r\nMaybe\r\nDetailed \r\nAnswer\r\nPossibly, but at what cost?\r\nSocial\r\nCool and measured.\r\nSocial\r\nRole\r\n  Asset\r\nContext\r\n  Formal Gathering\r\nChoice\r\n  Subject Info\r\nResult\r\n  Challenges You\r\nCombat\r\nEvaluates the enemy’s capabilities.\r\n  Random Encounter\r\nFight a small group of easy random monsters, then a \r\nlarger group of those monsters joins \r\n  1d3 rounds \r\nlater.\r\nCombat\r\nOutcome\r\n  Maneuver\r\nCombat\r\nTargeting\r\n  Strongest\r\nRole\r\n  Controller\r\nRole Size\r\n  Elite\r\nStance\r\n  Ambushing\r\nQuest & Encounter\r\n  New Quest\r\nCount the people present at an event or who enter or \r\npass by a region.\r\n  Quest Development\r\nOne of the NPCs involved is perhaps not who they \r\nseem.\r\n  Reward\r\nCoins of special mintage.\r\n  Penalty\r\nParty is fined by the local authorities \r\n  5% of their \r\nliquid wealth.\r\nQuest\r\nArchetype\r\n  Obtain\r\nSub\r\n  Fetch\r\n13"
